issue.title: Create function that calculates study timing.
issue.body:
- input:
  - reference domain/date
  - comparison domain/date(s)
- output comparison domain with added study timing variable(s)

issue.title: Develop approach to study timing.
issue.body:
- ADaM: unneeded - study timing is already derived.
- SDTM: relatively straightforward:
  - Reference date: `DM.RFSTDTC`.
  - Domain date: `domain.__DT`, `domain.__STDT`, `domain.__ENDT`, etc.
  - Call function that calculates number of days from reference date.
- EDC:
  - Specify reference date and domain.
  - Specify domain date(s).
  - Call function that calculates number of days from reference date.

issue.body: Is it possible to increase median line height ?  currently i can only change median color
